Blocks.Text: "Look!" re went on earnestly. "You are not going
to write up Pericles in some way or other, are
you ?" "What is there to write up ?" 11 said
Bawley. "There are forty - three submarines in
the Navy - why should y pick on Serides?"
John eyed him steadily. "It's the Pancifal
business ( is' t it ?4 he said quietly
